snippet.title: Tabletop Simulator Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Tabletop Simulator has officially launched out of Early Access on Steam! 
Check it out: http://store.steampowered.com/app/286160

Website:
http://www.berserk-games.com

Tabletop Simulator is the only simulator where you can let your aggression out by flipping the table! There are no rules to follow: just you, a physics sandbox, and your friends. Make your own games and play how YOU want!

Credits:
Trailer created by Michael Clark

Mods:
Tabletop Minigolf by Riddix
Mancala by MrNobodyX3
Mikado Epic Eric and Berna
Tabletop Bowling by Riddix
Roulette Modeled (US/EU) V2.0! by =AJSA= Moneyman12167Casey
Wilderness Tile Playset (95 Pieces) by [RGC]MWMDragon
Tabletop Hockey by Riddix
Allegiance by djackthompson
Banana by NukeE
Tabletop Pool by Riddix
Table with sofa & wine & turkey by kimoyahoo (just changed name to RIO2016)
eyesor by gnomes

Song: Jazz In Paris
